cludes<strong> You</strong> as Scarlet's last hope...</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>🚩 </em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong><em>Trigger warning:</em></strong><em> Violence, First message includes the beginning of an assault. </em></span><strong><em>🚩</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 491px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_5a2364fb-b478-43d1-9e88-5d6c691dc59d.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 498px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_b36e676a-91c8-4b21-a4b3-39eccdb29f97.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꧁<strong>(Sound: </strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0wWeTbOBqyU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>ZZ ward, Kendrik Lamar - Cryin Wolf</strong></a><strong> (</strong><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/63q8MyDPEfsLZlas5oJw8Z?si=e236709c406f4ef2\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target